com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class ConnectionListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.CallListenerAdapter
      • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.ConnectionListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, CallListener, ConnectionListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CallControlConnectionListenerAdapter, TerminalConnectionListenerAdapter

    public class ConnectionListenerAdapter
extends CallListenerAdapter
implements ConnectionListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to the Connection object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    ConnectionListener
